---
import { Zap, CheckCircle2, Award, Clock, TrendingUp } from 'lucide-astro';
---

<section id="inicio" class="featured-treatment">
    <div class="container treatment-container">
        <div class="treatment-content">
            <span class="badge">Tecnología de Vanguardia en Urología</span>
            <h1 class="treatment-title">HoLEP: Cirugía de Próstata con Láser de Holmio</h1>
            <p class="treatment-description">
                <strong>El estándar de oro para el tratamiento del agrandamiento de próstata.</strong> 
                HoLEP (Holmium Laser Enucleation of the Prostate) utiliza un láser de holmio de alta precisión 
                para eliminar completamente el tejido prostático que obstruye el flujo urinario, ofreciendo 
                resultados duraderos con mínima invasión.
            </p>
            
            <ul class="benefits-list">
                <li>
                    <CheckCircle2 class="check-icon" size={20} />
                    <span><strong>Sin incisiones externas</strong> - Procedimiento mínimamente invasivo a través de la uretra</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <CheckCircle2 class="check-icon" size={20} />
                    <span><strong>Recuperación rápida</strong> - Alta hospitalaria en 24-48 horas, retorno a actividades en 2 semanas</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <CheckCircle2 class="check-icon" size={20} />
                    <span><strong>Resultados duraderos</strong> - Bajo riesgo de reintervención comparado con otros métodos</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <CheckCircle2 class="check-icon" size={20} />
                    <span><strong>Mínimo sangrado</strong> - Seguro para pacientes que toman anticoagulantes</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <CheckCircle2 class="check-icon" size={20} />
                    <span><strong>Para próstatas de cualquier tamaño</strong> - Efectivo incluso en casos severos (>100g)</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <CheckCircle2 class="check-icon" size={20} />
                    <span><strong>Preserva la función sexual</strong> - Alta tasa de preservación de la función eréctil</span>
                </li>
            </ul>

            <div class="stats-row">
                <div class="stat">
                    <Award class="stat-icon" size={24} />
                    <div>
                        <strong>95%</strong>
                        <span>Tasa de éxito</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat">
                    <Clock class="stat-icon" size={24} />
                    <div>
                        <strong>1-2 días</strong>
                        <span>Hospitalización</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat">
                    <TrendingUp class="stat-icon" size={24} />
                    <div>
                        <strong>Duradero</strong>
                        <span>Resultados a largo plazo</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="treatment-actions">
                <a href="#contacto" class="btn btn-primary">Agendar Evaluación HoLEP</a>
                <a href="#holep-info" class="btn btn-text">Más sobre HoLEP &rarr;</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="treatment-visual">
            <div class="image-card">
                <img 
                    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1579684385127-1ef15d508118?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" 
                    alt="Tecnología láser de holmio para cirugía de próstata HoLEP - Tratamiento mínimamente invasivo" 
                    class="main-image"
                    loading="eager"
                />
                <div class="feature-badge">
                    <Zap class="feature-icon" />
                    <span>Láser de Holmio YAG</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .featured-treatment {
        padding: 6rem 0 4rem;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, #f0f9ff 0%, #ffffff 100%);
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .treatment-container {
        display: grid;
        gap: 4rem;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .treatment-content {
        max-width: 600px;
    }

    .badge {
        display: inline-block;
        background: var(--color-bg-light);
        color: var(--color-primary-dark);
        padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .treatment-title {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        line-height: 1.1;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--color-secondary), var(--color-primary));
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .treatment-description {
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        color: var(--color-text);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .benefits-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0 0 2.5rem 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .benefits-list li {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: var(--color-secondary);
    }

    .check-icon {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .stats-row {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(120px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    .stat {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .stat-icon {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .stat div {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.25rem;
    }

    .stat strong {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-family: var(--font-heading);
        color: var(--color-secondary);
        line-height: 1;
    }

    .stat span {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--color-text-light);
        line-height: 1;
    }

    .treatment-actions {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn-text {
        color: var(--color-text-light);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    .btn-text:hover {
        color: var(--color-primary);
    }

    /* Visual Side */
    .image-card {
        position: relative;
        border-radius: 24px;
        box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        padding: 1rem;
        background: white;
        transform: rotate(-2deg);
        transition: transform 0.5s ease;
    }

    .image-card:hover {
        transform: rotate(0deg);
    }

    .main-image {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 16px;
        display: block;
    }

    .feature-badge {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 2rem;
        right: -1rem;
        background: var(--color-secondary);
        color: white;
        padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 16px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.2);
        transform: rotate(2deg);
    }

    .feature-icon {
        color: #fbbf24; /* Gold/Yellow for laser energy */
    }

    @media (min-width: 992px) {
        .treatment-container {
            grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
        }

        .featured-treatment {
            padding: 8rem 0 6rem;
        }

        .treatment-title {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
        }
    }
</style>